fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 lost 57.80 points or 0.32% to settle at 18,089.85. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, fell 0.48% to 11.84. Adani Enterprises, Manappuram Finance and ICICI Bank were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The May 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 May 2023.
